subject: How to overwriter TestResult?
msgSnippet: Hello I want to overwrite TestResult. After executing my test I want to print the result of the test. The result should include following information: * each
messageBody:
Hello

I want to overwrite TestResult. After executing my test I want to print the
result of the test. The result should include following information:
* each test should have short description
* the duration of each test
* the result of each test, that means either OK or the failure oder error
message

Thanks a lot,
Juergen
